      <h4>Hello,</h4>
      <p>We hope you are doing OK in these challenging times and welcome to the latest issue of the Justia Jobs newsletter. A couple of brief notes:</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bullet-list" responsive="mobile-padding-horizontal-sides">
      {{#table class="set-max-width"}}
        <tr>
          <td class="bullet">
