            <p>If you apply for one of these jobs please indicate that you learned about it via Justia.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="bullet">
            {{>img src="https://justatic.com/emails/images/legal-jobs-newsletters/common/jobs-bullet-01.png" alt="bullet"}}
          </td>
          <td class="text">
            <p>If your organization is hiring you can contact us at <a href="mailto:legaljobs@justia.com" target="_blank"><b>legaljobs@justia.com</b></a> for details on how your job can be included in the next issue.</p>
