    <td class="description -last" responsive="mobile-padding-horizontal-sides">
      <p>We will continue publishing this newsletter and are evaluating additional ways to support job seekers during these times. Justia has also recently published <a href="https://www.justia.com/covid-19/50-state-covid-19-resources/coronavirus-and-unemployment-benefits-50-state-resources/" target="_blank"><b>a resource page on unemployment benefits</b></a> that are available due to COVID-19.</p>
      <p>This new service is a work in progress and we welcome your feedback at <a href="mailto:legaljobs@justia.com" target="_blank"><b>legaljobs@justia.com</b></a>.</p>
      <p>Best, <br>Justia Legal Jobs Team</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
{{/table}}
